hadiths[160]{hadithnumber,text}:
3489,aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aayat ( وجعلناكم شعوبا وقبائل‏ (ke mutaalliq farmaya ke (shuoob) badey qabeelon ke mana mein hai aur (qabaayel) se kisi badey qabeeley ki shakhein murad hain.
3490,"aik martaba puchha gaya : ya Rasulullah! sabse zyada sharif kon hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo sabse zyada parhezgaar ho.'' sahaba ne arz kya ke hamara sawal iske barey mein nahi hai, is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''phir (nasb ki ru se) Allah ke Nabi Yusuf (Alaihissalam) sabse zyada sharif they.''"
3491,"mujh se Zenab binte- abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zer parwarish reh chuki thin, Kaleeb ne bayan kya ke hamne Zenab se puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka talluq qabila Muzar se tha? unhon-ne kaha phir kis qabeele se tha? yaqinan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabila Muzar ki shaakh bani nazar bin kinaana ki aulad mein se they."
3492,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dubbaa, hantam, naqeer aur muzaffat ke istemal se mana farmaya tha aur maine unse puchha tha ke aap mujhey bataiye ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka talluq kis qabeele se tha? kya waqei aap ka talluq qabila Muzar se tha? unhon-ne kaha phir aur kis se ho sakta hai yaqinan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka talluq usi qabeele se tha. aap nazar-banii-bin-kinaana ki aulad mein se they."
3493,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum insanon ko kaan ki tarah paogey (bhalaaii aur burai mein) jo log jahiliyat ke zamaney mein behtar aur achi sifaat ke Malik they wo Islam laney ke baad bhi behtar aur achi sifaat waley hain basharte ke wo Deen ka ilm bhi hasil karein aur hukumat aur sardaarii ke laaiq usko paogey jo hukumat aur sardaarii ko bahut na-pasand karta ho.''
3494,"aur aadmiyon mein sabse bura usko paogey jo do-rukha ( doghla ( ho. un logon mein aik munh lekar aaey, dusron mein doosra munh."
3495,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''khilaafat ke mamley mein log Quraish ke taabe hain, aam musalman qureshi musalmanon ke taabe hain jis tarah unke aam kuffaar qureshi kuffaar ke taabe rahtey chaley aaey hain.''"
3496,"aur insanon ki misal kaan ki tarah hai, jo log jahiliyat ke daur mein sharif they wo Islam laney ke baad bhi sharif hain jabke unhon-ne Deen ki samajh bhi hasil ki ho tum dekhogey ke behtreen aur laaiq wahi Sabit hongey jo khilafat w imaarat ke ohdey ko bahut zyada na-pasand kartey rahe hon, yahan tak ke wo usmein giraftaar ho jaaein."
3497,unse Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ( إلا المودة في القربى‏ (ke mutaalliq (Taaoos ne) bayan kya ke Quraish ki koi shaakh aisi nahi thi jis main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qaraabat na rahi ho aur usi wjah se ye aayat nazil hui thi ke mera mutalba sirf ye hai ke tum log meri aur apni qarabat dari ka lihaaz karo.
3498,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''isii taraf se fitney uthein gey yani mashriq se aur bewafaaii aur sakht dillii un logon mein hai jo oonton aur gaayon ki dam ke paas chalaatey rahtey hain yani Rabee aur Muzar ke logon mein."""
3499,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke fakhr aur takabbur un cheekhney aur shor machaaney waley oont walon mein hai aur bakri charaney walon mein narm dillii aur mulaaimiyat hoti hai aur eman to Yaman mein hai hikmat ( hadis) bhi yamnii hai, abu-Adbullah yani (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke Yaman ka naam Yaman isliye hua ke ye Kaba ke daain taraf hai aur Sham ko Sham (Syria) isliye kehtey hain ke ye Kaba ke baain taraf hai. ( المشأمة ( baain taraf ko kehtey hain. baain hath ko) الشؤمى ( kehtey hain aur baain taraf ko) الأشأم‏ .) kehtey hain."
3500,Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) tak ye baat pahunchi jab wo Quraish ki aik jamat mein they ke Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ye hadis bayan kartey hain ke an-qareeb (qurbe-qiyaamat mein) bani qahtaan se aik hukmaraan uthega. ye sun kar Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ghussa ho gaey. phir aap khutba dene uthey aur Allah Taala ki uski shaan ke mutabiq hamd w sana ke baad farmaya : logo! mujhey malum hua hai ke kuchh log aisi hadisein bayan kartey hain jo na to Quran Majeed mein maujood hain aur na Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se manqul hain. dekho ! tum mein sabse jaahi yahi log hain. unse aur unke khayalat se bachtey raho jin khayalat ne unko gumrah kar diya hai. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye suna hai ke ye khilafat Quraish mein rahegi aur jo bhi unse dushmanii karega Allah Taala usko sir-nigun aur aundha kar dega jab tak wo (Quraish) Deen ko qaaim rakhengey.
3501,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ye khilafat us waqt tak Quraish ke hathon mein baqi rahegi jab tak ke unmein 2 aadmi bhi baqi rahein.''
3502,main aur Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) donon mil kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaey aur ham ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! banu-muttalib ko to aap ne ata farmaya aur hamein ( bani Umayya ko) nazar andaz kar diya halanke aap ke liye ham aur wo aik hi darjey ke hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' (ye sahi hai) magar banu-Haashim aur banu-matlab aik hi hain.''
3503,Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) bani zohra ke chand logon ke sath Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaey. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bani zohra ke sath bahut achi tarah pesh aati thin kyonke un logon ki Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se qaraabat thi.
3504,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Quraish, ansaar, juhaina, muzena, Aslam, ashja' aur ghifaar in sab qabeelon ke log mere khair-khaah hain aur unka bhi Allah aur uske rasool ke siwa koi himaayatii nahi hai.''"
3505,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke baad Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko sabse zyada mohabbat thi. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki aadat thi ke Allah Taala ki taraf se jo rizq bhi unko milta wo usey sadqa kar diya karti thin. Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( kisi se) kaha Ummul-Momenin ko is se roknaa chahiye (jab Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko unki baat pahunchii) to unhon-ne kaha : kya ab mere hathon ko rokaa jaeyga ab agar maine Abdullah se baat ki to mujh par nazar wajib hai. Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ko razi karne ke liye) Quraish ke chand logon aur khas taur se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke naanihaalii rishte-daaron (banu-zohra) ko unki khidmat mein maafi ki sifarish ke liye bheja lekin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) phir bhi na maaniin. is par banu-zohra ne jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke maamun hotey they aur unmein Abdur-Rehman bin Aswad-bin-abd-Yaghoos aur Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke jab ham unki ijazat se wahan ja baithein to tum aik baar aan kar parde mein ghus jao. chunanche unhon-ne aisa hi kya (jab Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) khush ho gain to ( unhon-ne unki khidmat mein das ghulam ( aazad karaaney ke liye bataur kaffara qism ( bhejey aur Ummul-Momenin ne unhein aazad kar diya. phir aap barabar ghulam aazad karti rahiin. yahan tak ke chalis (40) ghulam aazad kar diye phir unhon-ne kaha kash! maine jis waqt qism khaaii thi (mannat maana thi) to main koi khas cheez bayan kar deti jis ko karke mein farigh ho jati."
3506,"Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Zaid-bin-Saabit , Abdullah-bin-Zubair , Saeed bin Aas aur Abdur-Rehman bin Haris-bin-Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya (aur unko Quran Majeed ki kitabat par muqarrar farmaya, chunanche un hazraat ne) Quran Majeed ko kai kitaabon mein naql farmaya aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne (un charon mein se) teen qureshi sahaba se farmaya tha ke jab aap logon ka Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se (jo Madina Munawra ke rehney waley they) Quran ke kisi maqam par (iske kisi muhaawrey mein) ikhtilaf ho jaey to usko Quraish ke muhaawrey ke mutabiq likhnaa, kyonke Quran sharif Quraish ke muhaaware mein nazil hua hai. unhon-ne aisa hi kya."
3507,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabila Aslam ke sahaba ki taraf se guzrey jo bazar mein teer andazi kar rahe they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey aulaade-Ismaaeel! khub teer andazi karo ke tumharey bap Ismail (Alaihissalam) bhi teerandaaz they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya main falan jamat ke sath hun, ye sun kar dusri jamat walon ne hath rok liye to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya baat huii? unhon-ne arz kya ke jab aap doosrey fareeq ke sath ho gaey to phir ham kaisey teer andazi karein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum teer-andaazii jari rakho. main tum sab ke sath hun."
3508,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ''jis shakhs ne bhi jaan-bojh kar apne bap ke siwa kisi aur ko apna bap banaya to usne kufr kya aur jis shakhs ne bhi apna nasb kisi aisi qaum se milaya jis se uska koi (nasbi (rishtey ka ( ( talluq nahi hai to wo apna thikana jahannam mein bana ley.''"
3509,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sabse bada bohtan aur sakht jhoot ye hai ke aadmi apne bap ke siwa kisi aur ko apna bap kahey ya jo cheez us ne khuwab mein nahi dekhi. iske dekhney ka dawa kare. ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf aisi hadis mansub karey jo aap ne na farmai ho.''
3510,"qabila abdul-Qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur us ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! hamara talluq qabila Rabee se hai aur hamarey aur aap ke darmyan (raastey mein) kuffaar Muzar ka qabila padta hai, isliye ham aap ki khidmate-aqdas mein sirf hurmat ke mahinon mein hi hazir ho saktey hain. munasib hota agar aap hamein aisey ehkaam batla detey jin par ham khud bhi mazbootii se qaaim rahtey aur jo log hamarey peechhey reh gaey hain unhein bhi bata detey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhen char chizon ka hukm deta hun aur char chizon se roktaa hun, awwal Allah par eman laney ka, yani uski gawahi dena ke Allah Taala ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi aur Namaz qaaim karne ka aur zakat ada karne ka aur is baat ka ke jo kuchh bhi tumhen maale-ghanimat miley usmein se panchwan hissey Allah ko (yani imam waqt ke baitul-maal ko) ada karo aur main tumhen dubbaa, hantam, naqeer aur muzaffat (ke iste'maal) se mana karta hun."
3511,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par farma rahe they ''aagaah ho jao us taraf se fasaad phootega.'' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mashriq ki taraf ishara karke ye jumla farmaya, jidhar se shaitan ka seeng tuloo hota hai."
3512,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Quraish, ansaar, juhaina, muzena, Aslam, ghifaar aur ashja' mere khair-khaah hain, aur Allah aur uske rasool ke siwa aur koi unka himaayati nahi.''"
3513,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne member par farmaya ''Qabeela ghifaar ki Allah Taala ne maghfirat farma di aur qabila Aslam ko Allah Taala ne salamat rakha aur qabila usba ne Allah Taala ki aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki.''
3514,'qabeela Aslam ko Allah Taala ne salamat rakha aur qabila ghifaar ki Allah Taala ne maghfirat farma di. ''
3515,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' bataao kya juhaina , muzena , Aslam aur ghifaar ke qabeeley bani Tameem , bani Asad , bani Abdullah-bin Ghatfan aur bani Aamir bin Sasa ke muqaabley mein behtar hain? ''eik shakhs ( Aqra-bin-Habis ( ne kaha ke wo to tabah w barbad huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, ye charon qabeeley banu-Tameem, banu-Asad, banu- Abdullah-bin Ghatfan aur banu-Aamir bin Sasa ke qabeelon se behtar hain."
3516,"Aqra-bin-Habis (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke aap se un logon ne bait ki hai ke jo haajiyon ka saman charaaya kartey they yani Aslam aur ghifaar aur muzena ke log , Muhammad-bin abi Yaqoob ne kaha ke main samajhta hun Abdur-Rehman ne juhaina ka bhi zikr kya, Shoba ne kaha ke ye shak Muhammad-bin-abii Yaqoob ko hua. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''batlaao Aslam , ghifaar , muzena , aur main samajhta hun ke juhaina ko bhi kaha ye charon qabeeley bani Tameem , bani Aamir aur Asad aur Ghatfan se behtar nahi hain? kya ye (jiska baad mein zikr hua) kharaab aur barbad nahi huey ?'' Aqraa ne kaha : haan , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qasam hai us zaat ki jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! ye unse behtar hain.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qabila Aslam, ghifaar, muzena aur juhaina ke kuchh log ya unhon-ne bayan kya ke muzena ke kuchh log ya ( bayan kya ke) juhaina ke kuchh log Allah Taala ke nazdeek ya bayan kya ke qiyamat ke din qabila Asad, Tameem , Hawazin aur Ghatfan se behtar hongey."
3517,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim nahi hogi jab tak ke qabila qahtaan mein aik aisa shakhs paida nahi hoga jo logon par apni laathii ke zor se hukumat karega.''
3518,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jihad mein Sharik they, muhajireen badi tadaad mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jama ho gaey. wjah ye hui ke muhajireen mein aik sahib they badey dil lagi karne waale, unhon-ne aik Ansari ke koolhey par chot lagai , Ansari bahut sakht ghussa hua. us ne apni braadrii walon ko madad ke liye pukara aur naubat yahan tak pahunchi ke un logon ne yani Ansari ne kaha : aey qabaayel Ansar ! madad ko pahuncho ! aur muhajir ne kaha : aey muhajireen ! madad ko pahuncho ! ye shor sun kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( kheme se) bahar tashrif laey aur farmaya : kya baat hai? ye jahiliyat ki pukar kaisi hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sura haal malum karne par muhajir sahabi ke Ansari sahabi ko mar dene ka waqia bayan kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisi jahiliyat ki napak baatein chhod do aur Abdullah-bin-Ubai salool ( munafiq ( ne kaha ke ye muhajireen ab hamarey khilaf apni qaum walon ki duhaaii dene lagey. Madina pahunch kar ham samajh lengey , izzat daar zaleel ko yaqinan nikal bahar kar dega. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ijazat chahi ya Rasulullah ! ham us napak paleed Abdullah-bin-Ubai ko qatl kyon na kar dein ? lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisa na hona chahiye ke log kahin ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne logon ko qatl kar diya kartey hain."
3519,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''wo shakhs ham mein se nahi hai jo ( nauha kartey huey) apne rukhsar peetey , garebaan phaad daaley, aur jahiliyat ki pukar pukaarey .''"
3520,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Amr-bin-Luhiy-bin-Qum'aa-bin-Khandaf qabila khuza'aa ka bap tha.''
3521,(baheera) wo ontni jiske doodh ki manaahii hoti thi. kyonke wo buton ke liye waqf hoti thi. isliye koi bhi shakhs iska doodh nahi dohataa tha aur (saayeba) usey kehtey jis ko wo apne ma'boodon ke liye chhod detey aur un par koi bojh na laadtaa aur na koi sawari karta. unhon-ne kaha ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''maine Amr-bin-Aamir-bin-Luhi Khuzai ko dekha ke jahannam mein wo apni antadiyaan ghaseet raha tha aur yahi Amr wo pahlaa shakhs hai jisne (saayeba) ki rasm nikaalii.''
3522,"jab Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nabwooat ke barey malum hua to unhon-ne apne bhai Anees se kaha Makka janey ke liye sawari taiyaar kar aur us shakhs ke mutaalliq jo Nabi honey ka muddaii hai aur kehta hai ke uske paas aasman se khabar aati hai, mere liye khabrein hasil karke laa. uski baton ko khud ghaur se sunnaa aur phir mere paas aanaa. unke bhai wahan se chaley aur Makka hazir ho kar aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baatein khud suniin phir wapas ho kar unhon-ne Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bataya ke maine unhein khud dekha hai, wo achchhey akhlaq ka logon ko hukm kartey hain aur maine unse jo kalam suna wo sher nahi hai. is par Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha jis maqsad ke liye maine tumhen bheja tha mujhey is par poori tarah itmeenaan nahi huaa. aakhir unhon-ne khud khane-pine ka saman baandhaa, pani se bharaa hua aik puraanaa mishkeeza sath liya aur Makka aaey. masjidul-haraam mein haziri di aur yahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko talash kya. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pehchantey nahi they aur kisi se aap ke mutaalliq poochhna bhi munasib nahi samjhaa, kuchh raat guzar gaee ke wo letey huey they, Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko us haalat mein dekha aur samajh gaey ke koi musaafir hai. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha aap mere ghar chal kar aaraam keejiye. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) unke peechhey peechhey chaley gaey lekin kisi ne aik doosrey ke barey mein baat nahi ki. jab subah hui to Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna mishkeeza aur khane-pine ka saman uthaya aur masjidul-haraam mein aa gaey. ye din bhi yoonhii guzar gaya aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko na dekh sakey. Sham hui to soney ki taiyaarii karne lagey. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) phir wahan se guzrey aur samajh gaey ke abhi apne thikaaney janey ka waqt us shakhs par nahi aaya, wo unhein wahan se phir apne sath ley aaey aur aaj bhi kisi ne aik doosrey se baat cheet nahi ki, tesraa din jab hua aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke sath yahi kaam kya aur apne sath le gaey to unse puchha kya tum mujhey bata saktey ho ke yahan aaney ki wajah kya hai? Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar tum mujh se pukhta wada kar lo ke meri rehnumai karogey to main tum ko sab kuchh bata doonga. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne wada kar liya to unhon-ne unhein apne khayalat ki khabar di. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke bila shubah wo haq par hain aur Allah ke sachey rasool hain achchha subah ko tum mere peechhey peechhey mere sath chalnaa. agar main (raastey mein) koi aisi baat dekhun jis se mujhey tumharey barey mein koi khatrah ho to main khada ho jaaunga (kisi diwar ke qareeb) maano mujhey peshab karna hai. us waqt tum mera intizar mat karna aur jab main phir chalney lagoon to mere peechhey aa jana taake koi samajh na sakey ke ye donon sath hain aur is tarah jis ghar mein, main dakhil hon tum bhi dakhil ho jaanaa. unhon-ne aisa hi kya aur peechhey peechhey chaley yahan tak ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunch gaey, aap ki baatein suniin aur wahin Islam ley aaey. phir aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya : ab apni qaum ghifaar mein wapas jao aur unhein mera haal bataao yahan tak ke jab hamarey ghalbe ka ilm tumko ho jaey (to phir hamarey paas aa jana) Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, main un Qureshiyon ke majme' mein pukar kar kalima tauheed ka elaan karunga. chunanche aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan se wapas wo masjide-haraam mein aaey aur buland awaz se kaha ke ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur ye ke Muhammad Allah ke rasool hain ''ye suntey hi un par Sara majma' toot padaa aur sab ne unhein itna maara ke zameen par lita diya. itney mein Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aagey aur Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ke uper apne ko daal kar Quraish se unhon-ne kaha afsos! kya tumhen malum nahi ke ye shakhs qabila ghifaar se hai aur Sham (Syria) janey waley tumharey taajiron ka rasta udhar hi se padta hai, is tarah se unse unko bachaayaa. phir Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) doosrey din masjide-haraam mein aaey aur apne Islam ka izhar kya. qaum phir buri tarah un par toot padi aur maarney lagey. us din bhi Abbas un par aundhey pad gaey. kya main Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ke Islam ka waqia tumhen sunaun? ham ne arz kya zaroor sunaaiye. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya . mera talluq qabila ghifaar se tha. hamarey yahan ye khabar pahunchi thi ke Makka mein aik shakhs paida huey hain jinka dawa hai ke wo Nabi hain. (pahley to) maine apne bhai se kaha ke us shakhs ke paas Makka ja , us se guftgu kar aur phir iske sarey halaat aa kar mujhey bataa. chunanche mere bhai khidmat nabwi mein hazir huey aur aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mulaqat ki aur wapas aa gaey. maine puchha ke kya khabar laaey? unhon-ne kaha, Allah ki qasam! maine aisey shakhs ko dekha hai jo achchhey kaamon ke liye kehta hai aur burey kaamon se mana karta hai. maine kaha ke tumhari baton se to mujhey itmeenaan nahi huaa. ab maine toshey ka thailaa aur chhadi uthai aur Makka aa gaya. wahan mein kisi ko pehchanta nahi tha aur aap ke mutaalliq kisi se poochhtey huey bhi dar lagta tha. main ( sirf ( zamzam ka pani pi liya karta tha, aur masjide-haraam mein thehra hua tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke aik martaba Ali (Raziallahu anhu) mere samney se guzrey aur boley malum hota hai ke aap is Shahar mein musaafir hain. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine kaha : ji haan. bayan kya ke to phir mere ghar chalo. phir wo mujhey apne ghar sath ley gaey. bayan kya ke main aap ke saath-saath gaya. na unhon-ne koi baat poochhi aur na maine kuchh kaha, subah hui to main phir masjide-haraam mein aa gaya taake aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein kisi se poochhoon lekin aap ke barey mein koi bataaney wala nahi tha. bayan kya ke phir Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) mere samney se guzrey aur boley ke kya abhi tak aap apne thikaaney ko nahi pa sakey hain? bayan kya, maine kaha ke nahi. unhon-ne kaha ke achchha phir mere sath aaiye , unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne poochha. aap ka matlab kya hai. aap us Shahar mein kyon aaey? unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine kaha : aap agar zahir na karein to main aapko apne mamley ke barey mein bataaun . unhon-ne kaha ke main aisa hi karunga. tab maine unse kaha, hamein malum hua hai ke yahan koi shakhs paida huey hain jo nabwooat ka dawa kartey hain. maine pahley apne bhai ko unse baat karne ke liye bheja tha. lekin jab wo wapas huey to unhon-ne mujhey koi itmeenaan bakhsh khabrein nahi dein. isliye main is irade se aaya hun ke unse khud mulaqat karun. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aap ne achchha rasta paya ke mujh se mil gaey. main unhiin ke paas ja raha hun. aap mere peechhey-peechhey chalein . jahan mein dakhil hon aap bhi dakhil ho jaaein. agar main kisi aisey aadmi ko dekhunga jis se aap ke barey mein mujhey khatrah hoga to main kisi diwar ke paas khada ho jaunga, maano ke main apna jootaa theek kar raha hun. us waqt aap aagey badh jana chunanche wo chaley aur main bhi unke peechhey ho liya aur aakhir mein wo aik makan ke andar gaey aur main bhi unke sath Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein andar dakhil ho gaya. maine aanhazrat (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke Islam ke usool w arkaan mujhey samjha dijiye. aap ne mere samney unki wazaahat farmaiye aur main musalman ho gaya. phir aap ne farmaya : aey abu-Zar! us mamley ko abhi posheeda rakhna aur apne Shahar ko chaley jaanaa. phir jab tumhen hamarey ghalbe ka haal malum ho jaey tab yahan dobara aanaa. maine arz kya us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath maboos kya hai main to un sab ke samney Islam ke kalima ka elaan karunga. chunanche wo masjidul-haraam mein aaey. Quraish ke log wahan maujood they aur kaha, aey Quraish ki jama'at! (suno) mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad uske bandey aur uske rasool hain. (quraishiyon ne kaha ke us bd-deen ki khabar lo. chunanche wo meri taraf lapkey aur mujhey itna maara ke main marney ke qareeb ho gaya. itney mein Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aagey aur mujh par gir kar mujhey apne jism se chipa liya aur quraishiyon ki taraf mutwajjeh ho kar unhoney kaha, arey naadaano! qabila ghifaar ke aadmi ko qatl kartey ho. ghifaar se to tumhari tijarat bhi hai aur tumharey qafley bhi us taraf se guzartey hain. is par unhon-ne mujhey chhod diya. phir jab dusri subah hui to phir main masjide-haraam mein aaya aur jo kuchh maine kal pukara tha usi ko phir dohraayaa. quraishiyon ne phir kaha : pakdo us bd-deen ko. jo kuchh unhon-ne mere sath kal kya tha wahi aaj bhi kya. ittifaq se phir Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib aagey aur mujh par gir kar mujhey apne jism se unhon-ne chipa liya aur jaisa unhon-ne quraishiyon se kal kaha tha waisaa hi aaj bhi kaha, Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ke Islam qabool karne ki shuruaat is tarah se hui thii."
3523,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qabeela Aslam, ghifaar aur muzena aur Juhaina ke kuchh log ya unhon-ne bayan kya ke muzena ke kuchh log ya (bayaan kya ke) juhaina ke kuchh log Allah Taala ke nazdeek ya bayan kya ke qiyamat ke din qabila Asad , Tameem , Hawazin aur Ghatfan se behtar hongey. ''"
3524,"agar tum ko Arab ki jahaalat malum karna achchha lagey to sura Al-Anaam mein aik so tees aayaton ke baad ye aayatein padh lo قد خسر الذين قتلوا أولادهم سفها بغير علم''yaqeenan wo log tabah huey jinhoney apni aulad ko naadaanii se mar dala. '' se lekar (قد ضلوا وما كانوا مهتدين) ''wo gumrah hain, raah paaney waley nahi.'' tak."
3525,jab (sura Shau'raa ki) ye aayat utri ( وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين‏ ( ''aey paighambar ! apne qaribi rishte-daaron ko daraa.'' to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Quraish ke mukhtalif qabeelon ko bulaya aey bani fahar! aey bani adii! jo Quraish ke khandan they.
3526,jab ye aayat ( وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين‏ ( ''aur aap apne qaribi rishte-daaron ko daraaiye.'' utri to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne alag alag qabaayel ko dawat di.
3527,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Abd-Manaaf ke beto! apni jaanon ko Allah se khareed lo (yani nek kaam karke unhein Allah Taala ke azab se bacha lo ( . aey abdul-Muttalib ke beto ! apni jaanon ko Allah Taala se khareed lo. aey Zubair-bin-Awaam ki walida ! Rasulullah ki phoophii , aey Fatima binte- Muhammad ! tum donon apni jaanon ko Allah se bacha lo. main tumharey liye Allah ki bargah mein kuchh ikhtiyar nahi rakhta. tum donon mere maal mein jitna chaho maang sakti ho.''"
3528,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ko khas taur se aik martaba bulaayaa, phir unse puchha kya tum logon mein koi aisa shakhs bhi rehta hai jiska talluq tumharey qabeeley se na ho? unhon-ne arz kya ke sirf hamara aik bhanja aisa hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bhanja bhi usi qaum mein dakhil hota hai."
3529,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) unke yahan tashrif laey to wahan (ansaar ki) 2 ladkiyan daf bajaa kar ga rahi thin. ye Haj ke dinon Mina ka waqia hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chehrey par kapda daley huey letey they Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein daantaa to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne chehre se kapda hata kar farmaya ''abu-Bakar! unhein chhod do, ye eid ke din hain, ye Mina mein thaharney ke din they.''"
3530,"maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh ko parde mein rakhey huey hain aur main habshiyon ko dekh rahi thi jo nezon ka khel masjid mein kar rahe they Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein daantaa. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''unhein chhod do, bani arfada tum be-fikr ho kar khelo.''"
3531,"Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushrekeen ( Quraish (ka mazaaq udaaney ki ijazat chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir main bhi to un hi ke khandan se hun. is par Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke main aapko (she'r mein) is tarah saaf nikal ley jaaunga jaisey aatey mein se baal nikal liya jata hai. aur (Hishaam ne) apne walid se riwayat kya ke unhon-ne kaha, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan mein Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) ko bura kehney laga to unhon-ne farmaya, unhein bura na kaho, wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se bachaw kya kartey they."
3532,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere panch naam hain. main Muhammad, Ahmed aur maahii hun (yani mitaaney wala hun) ke Allah Taala mere zariey kufr ko mitaaeyga aur main haashir hun ke tamam insanon ka (qiyamat ke din) mere baad hashr hoga aur main aaqib hon yani khaatimunnabiyeen hun. mere baad koi nayaa paighambar duniya mein nahi aayega.''"
3533,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tumhein tajjub nahi hota ke Allah Taala mujh se Quraish ki gaaliyon aur laanat malaamat ko kis tarah door karta hai. mujhey wo ( مذمم ( keh kar bura kehtey, is par laanat kartey hain. halanke main to Muhammad hoon.''"
3534,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meri aur doosrey anbiya ki misal aisi hai jaise kisi shakhs ne koi ghar banaya, usey khub sajaa kar mukammal kar diya. sirf aik iint ki jagah khali chhod di. log us ghar mein dakhil hotey aur tajjub kartey aur kehtey kash! ye aik iint ki jagah khali na rehti to kaisa achchha mukammal ghar hotaa.''"
3535,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meri aur mujh se pahley ke tamam anbiya ki misal aisi hai jaisey aik shakhs ne aik ghar banaya aur is mein har tarah ki zeenat paida ki lekin aik koney mein aik iint ki jagah chhoot gaee. ab tamam log aatey hain aur makan ko charon taraf se ghoom kar dekhtey hain aur tajjub mein pad jatey hain lekin ye bhi kehtey jatey hain ke yahan par aik iint kyon na rakhi gaii? to main hi wo iint hun aur main khaatimunnabiyeen hoon.''
3536,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tiresath saal ki umr mein wafat paai aur ibne-Shahab ne kaha ke mujh se Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne isi tarah bayan kya.
3537,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bazar mein they ke aik sahib ki awaz aai. ya abul-Qasim! aap unki taraf mutwajjeh huey ( malum hua ke unhon-ne kisi aur ko pukara hai) is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' mere naam par naam rakho lekin meri kunniyat mat rakho.''
3538,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere naam par naam rakha karo lekin meri kunniyat na rakha karo.''
3539,abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere naam par naam rakho lekin meri kunniyat na rakha karo.''
3540,"maine Saaib-bin-Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) ko 94 saal ki umr mein dekha ke khaasey qawii w tawaanaa they. unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey yaqin hai ke mere kanon aur aankhon se jo main nafa hasil kar raha hun wo sirf Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dua ki barkat hai. meri khala mujhey aik martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein le gain aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! ye mera bhanja bimar hai, aap uske liye dua farma dein. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere liye dua farmai."
3541,"meri khala mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein lekar hazir huin aur unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mera bhanja bimar ho gaya hai. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere sar par hath phera aur mere liye barkat ki dua farmai. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu ka pani piyaa, phir aap ki peeth ki taraf ja ke khada ho gaya aur maine nabwooat ki mehar ko aap ke donon moondhon ke beech dekha Muhammad-bin Ubaidullah ne kaha ke) حجلة ), Mina ( حجل الفرس ( se liya gaya hai jo ghodey ki us safedi ko kehtey hain jo uski donon aankhon ke beech mein hoti hai."
3542,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Asr ki Namaz se farigh ho kar masjid se bahar nikley to dekha ke Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) bachchon ke sath khel rahe hain. aap ne unko apne kandhey par bitha liya aur farmaya : mere bap tum par qurbaan hon tum mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki shakl milti hai. Ali ki nahi. ye sun kar Ali (Raziallahu anhu) hans rahe they (khush ho rahe they).
3543,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maine dekha tha. Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ki shakl aap ki shakl se poori tarah milti thi.
3544,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha hai, Hasan-bin-Ali (rz) ki shakl aap ki shakl se poori tarah milti thii. Ismail bin abi Khalid ne kaha, maine abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) se arz kya ke aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sifat bayan karein. unhon-ne kaha aap safaid rang ke they, kuchh baal safaid ho gaey they aur aap ne hamein 13 oontniyon ke diye janey ka hukm kya tha. lekin abhi ham ne un oontniyon ko apne qabze mein bhi nahi liya tha ke aap ki wafat ho gaee."
3545,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nichley hont Mubarak ke nichey thodii ke kuchh baal safaid they.
3546,"aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi Abdullah-bin Basar (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) boodhey ho gaey they? unhon-ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki thodi ke chand baal safaid ho gaey they."
3547,"maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khubiyan bayan kartey huey batlaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) beech ke qad ke they. na bahut lambey aur na chhotey qad waley . rang khultaa hua tha ( surkh w safaid ( na khali safaid they aur na bilkul gehunwey rang key. aap ke baal na bilkul mudey huey sakht qism ke they aur na seedhey latkey huey hi they. wahi nazil honey ke waqt aap ki umr chalis (40) saal thi. Makka mein aap ne das saal tak qiyam farmaya aur us poorey arse mein aap par wahi nazil hoti rahi aur Madina mein bhi aap ka qiyam das saal tak raha. aap ke sar aur dadhi mein bees baal bhi safaid nahi huey they. Rabee (raawii hadis) ne bayan kya ke phir maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aik baal dekha to wo laal tha maine iske mutaalliq puchha to mujhey bataya gaya ke khushbu lagaatey lagaatey laal ho gaya hai."
3548,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) na bahut lambey they aur na chhotey qad ke, na bilkul safaid they aur na gehunwey rang ke. na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baal bahut zyada ghunghraaley they aur na bilkul seedhey latkey huey, Allah Taala ne aapko chalis (40) saal ki umr mein nabwooat di aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Makka mein das saal tak qiyam kya aur Madina mein das saal tak qiyam kya. jab Allah Taala ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko wafat di to aap ke sar aur dadhi ke bees baal bhi safaid nahi they."
3549,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Husn w jamaal mein bhi sabse badh kar they aur jismani saakht mein bhi sabse behtar they. aap ka qad na bahut lamba tha aur na chhota ( balke darmyaana qad thaa).
3550,maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi khizaab bhi istemal farmaya tha? unhon-ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi khizaab nahi lagaya. sirf Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki donon kanpatiyon par (sar mein) chand baal safaid they.
3551,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) darmyaana qad ke they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka Sina bahut kushaada aur khula hua tha. aap ke (sar ke) baal kanon ki lo tak lataktey rahtey they. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik martaba aik surkh jodey mein dekha. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se badh kar Husain kisi ko nahi dekha tha. yoosuf-bin-abii-Is'haaq ne apne walid ke waaste se (إلى منكبيه‏) bayan kya (bajaaey lafz ( شحمة أذنه ( yani aap ke baal moondhon tak pahunchtey they.
3552,"kisi ne Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra talwaar ki tarah ( lamba patlaa ( tha? unhon-ne kaha nahi, chehra Mubarak chaand ki tarah ( gol aur khoobsurat ( tha."
3553,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) do-pahar ke waqt safar ke irade se nikley. Batha naam ke jagah par pahunch kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur Zohar ki Namaz 2 rakaat ( qasr ( padhi phir Asr ki bhi 2 rakaat ( qasr ( padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik chhota sa neza ( bataur sutrah ( gadaa hua tha. Aun ne apne walid se is riwayat mein ye zyada kya hai ke abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke us neze ke aagey se aaney janey waley aa ja rahe they. phir sahaba aap ke paas aagey aur aap ke Mubarak hathon ko thaam kar apne chehron par pherney lagey. abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath ko apne chehrey par rakha. us waqt wo barf se bhi zyada thanda aur mashk se bhi zyada khushbu daar tha.
3554,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sabse zyada data they aur Ramazan mein jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ki mulaqat hoti to aap ki sakhawat aur bhi badh jaya karti thi. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) Ramazan ki har raat mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mulaqat ke liye tashrif latey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Quran Majeed ka daur kartey. us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khair w bhalai ke mamley mein tez chalney wali hawa se bhi zyada data ho jatey they.
3555,"aik martaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahan bahut hi khush khush dakhil huey, khushi aur musarrat se peshani ki lakeerein chamak rahi thin. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Aaisha! tum ne suna nahi Mudliji ne Zaid w Usama ke sirf qadam dekh kar kya baat kahii? usne kaha ke aik ke paon doosrey ke paon se miltey huey nazar aatey hain.''"
3556,"aap jange-Tabook main apne peechhey reh janey ka waqia bayan kar rahe they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir maine ( tauba qabool honey ke baad) hazir ho kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya to chehra musarrat w khushi se chamak raha tha. jab bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi baat par khush hotey to chehra chamak uthtaa, aisa malum hota jaisey chaand ka tukda ho aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khushi ko ham usi se pehchan jatey they."
3557,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main ( Adam (Alaihissalam) se lekar ( barabar aadmiyon ke behtar zamanon mein hota aaya hun (yani sharif aur pakeeza naslon mein) yahan tak ke wo zamana aaya jis mein main paida hua.''
3558,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (sar ke aagey ke baalon ko peshani par) padaa rehney detey they aur mushrekeen ki ye aadat thi ke wo aagey ke sar ke baal 2 hisson mein taqseem kar letey they (peshaanii par padaa nahi rehney detey they) aur ahle-kitab (yahood w nasaaraa) sar ke aagey ke baal peshani par padaa rehney detey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un muaamlon mein jinke mutaalliq Allah Taala ka koi hukm aapko na mila hota. ahle-kitab ki muwafiqat pasand farmatey (aur hukm nazil honey ke baad wahi par amal kartey they) phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi sar mein maang nikalney lagey.
3559,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bad-zabaan aur ladney jhagadney waley nahi they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they ke tum mein sabse behtar wo shakhs hai jiske akhlaq sabse achchhey hon (jo logon se muskuraa kar pesh aaey).
3560,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jab bhi 2 chizon mein se kisi aik ke ikhtiyar karne ke liye kaha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamesha usi ko ikhtiyar farmaya jis mein aapko zyada aasani malum hoti basharte ke usmein koi gunah na ho. kyonke agar usmein gunah ka koi shubah bhi hota to aap us se sabse zyada door rahtey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni zaat ke liye kabhi kisi se badla nahi liya. lekin agar Allah ki hurmat ko koi todtaa to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us se zaroor badla letey they.
3561,na to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hatheli se zyada narm w naazuk koi hareer w deebaaj mere hathon ne kabhi chhuwa aur na maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khushbu se zyada behtar aur pakeeza koi khushbu ya atr soonghaa .
3562,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) parda nasheenii kunwari ladkiyon se bhi zyada sharmeeley they.
3563,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kabhi kisi khaney mein aib nahi nikaalaa, agar aapko marghoob hota to khaatey warna chhod detey."
3564,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab sajda kartey to donon hath pet se alag rakhtey yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baghlein ham log dekh letey, ibne-Bukair ne bakr se riwayat ki usmein yun hai, yahan tak ke aap ki baghlon ki safedi dikhai deti thi."
3565,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dua istisqaa (baarish k barasney ki dua) ke siwa aur kisi dua main (zyaada oonchaa) hath nahi uthatey they. is dua mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) itna uncha hath uthatey ke baghl ki safedi dikhai deti thi.
3566,"main safar ke irade se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abtah main ( Muhassab mein) khema ke andar tashrif rakhtey they. sakht do-pahar ka waqt tha. itney mein Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bahar nikal kar Namaz ke liye azan di aur andar aagey aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke wuzu ka bacha hua pani nikala to log usey leney ke liye toot padey. phir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik neza nikala aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laaey, maano aap ki pindliyon ki chamak ab bhi meri nazron ke samney hai. Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne (sutrah ke liye) neza gaad diya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar aur Asr ki 2-2 rakaat qasr Namaz padhai, gadhey aur auratein aap ke samney se guzar rahi thin."
3567,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) itney thahar-thahar kar baatein kartey ke agar koi shakhs (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke alfaaz) gin lena chahta to gin sakta tha.
3568,(abu-Huraira (rz)) par tumhen tajjub nahi hua. wo aaey aur mere hujre ke aik koney mein baith kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadison mujhey sunaney ke liye bayan karne lagey. main us waqt Namaz padh rahi thi. phir wo meri Namaz khatm honey se pahley hi uth kar chaley gaey. agar wo mujhey mil jatey to main unki khabar leti ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tumhari tarah yun jaldi-jaldi baatein nahi kya kartey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhen zahir mein soti thin lekin dil ghaafil nahi hota tha.
3569,"Ramazan sharif main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Namaz ( tahajjud ya Taraaveeh ( ki kya kaifiyat hoti thi? unhon-ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ramazaan mubaarak yaa doosrey kisi bhi mahiney mein gyara (11) rakaat se zyada nahi padhtey they (un hi ko tahajjud kaho ya Taraaveeh ( pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) char rakaat padhtey, wo rakatein kitni lambi hoti thin. kitni usmein khoobi hoti thin iske barey mein na poochho. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) char rakatein padhtey. ye charon bhi kitni lambi hotiin aur unmein kitni khoobi hoti. iske mutaalliq na poochho. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) teen rakaat witr padhtey, maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! aap witr padhney se pahley kyon so jatey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meri aankhen soti hain lekin mera dil bedaar rehta hai.''"
3570,"wo masjide-Haraam se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki meraaj ka waqia bayan kar rahe they ke) meraaj se pahley) teen Farishtey aaey. ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil honey se bhi pahley ka waqia hai. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjide-Haraam main ( 2 aadmiyon Hamza aur Jafar bin abii-Taalib ke darmyan ( so rahe they. aik Farishtey ne puchha : wo kon hain? ( jinko ley janey ka hukm hai) doosrey ne kaha ke wo darmyan waley hain. wahi sabse behtar hain. teesrey ne kaha ke phir jo sabse behtar hain unhein sath ley chalo. us raat sirf itna hi waqia ho kar reh gaya. phir aap ne unhein nahi dekha. lekin Farishtey aik aur raat mein aaey. aap dil ki nigaah se dekhtey they aur aap ki aankhen soti thin par dil nahi sota tha, aur tamam anbiya ki yahi kaifiyat hoti hai ke jab unki aankhen soti hain to dil us waqt bhi bedaar hota hai. gharaz ke phir Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne aapko apne sath liya aur aasman par chadhaa ley gaey."
3571,"wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they, raat bhar sab log chaltey rahe jab subah ka waqt qareeb hua to padao kya ( chunkey ham thakey huey they) isliye sab log itni gehri neend so gaey ke suraj poori tarah nikal aaya. sabse pahley Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) jaagey . lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko , jab aap sotey hotey to jagaatey nahi they yahan tak ke aap khud hi jaagtey. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi jaag gaey. aakhir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke sar Mubarak ke qareeb baith gaey aur buland awaz se Allahu-akbar kehney lagey. is se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi jaag gaey aur wahan se kooch ka hukm de diya. ( phir kuchh faasley par tashrif laey (aur yahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) utrey aur aap ne hamein subah ki Namaz padhai. aik shakhs ham se door koney mein betha raha. usney hamarey sath Namaz nahi padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz se farigh huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : aey falan ! hamarey sath Namaz padhney se tujhey kis cheez ne rokaa ? us ne arz kya ke mujhey ghusl ki haajat ho gaee hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey hukm diya ke paak mitti se tayammum kar lo ( phir usne bhi tayammum ke baad) Namaz padhi. Imran (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey chand sawaaron ke sath aagey bhej diya. (taake pani talash karein kyonke ( hamein sakht piyaas lagi hui thi, ab ham usi haalat mein chal rahe they ke hamein aik aurat mili jo 2 mushkon ke darmyan ( sawari par) apne paon latkaey huey ja rahi thi. ham ne us se kaha ke pani kahan milta hai? us ne jawab diya ke yahan pani nahi hai. ham ne us se puchha ke tumharey ghar se pani kitney faasley par hai? us ne jawab diya ke aik din aik raat ka fasla hai, ham ne us se kaha ke achchha tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein chalo , wo bolii Rasulullah ke kya mana hain? Imran (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, aakhir ham usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laaey, us ne aap se bhi wahi kaha jo ham se keh chuki thi. haan itna aur kaha ke wo yateem bachchon ki maan hai (is liye waajibe-raham hai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se uske donon mishkezon ko utara gaya aur aap ne unke dahaanon par hath pheraa. ham chalis (40) piyaasey aadmiyon ne usmein se khub sairaab ho kar piyaa aur apne tamam mishkeezey aur baaltiyaan bhi bhar lin sirf ham ne oonton ko pani nahi pilaayaa, iske bawajud uski mashkein pani se itni bhari hui thin ke malum hota tha abhi bah padengii. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo kuchh tumharey paas hai (khaaney ki chizon mein se) mere paas laao. chunanche us aurat ke liye roti ke tukdey aur khajoorein la kar jama kar diin gaiin. phir jab wo apne qabeeley mein aai to apne aadmiyon se usne kaha ke aaj main sabse badey jadoo gar se mil kar aai hon ya phir jaisa ke (iske manney waale) log kehtey hain, wo waqei Nabi hai. aakhir Allah Taala ne iske qabeeley ko usi aurat ki wjah se hidayat di, wo khud bhi Islam laai aur tamam qabeeley walon ne bhi Islam qabool kar liya."
3572,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik bartan hazir kya gaya (paanii ka ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt (Madina ke nazdeek) maqam Zauraa mein tashrif rakhtey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us bartan mein hath rakha to usmein se pani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyon ke darmyan se phootney laga aur usi pani se poori jamat ne wuzu kya. Qatada ne kaha ke maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aap log kitni tadaad mein they? unhon-ne farmaya ke teen so rahe hongey ya teen so ke qareeb rahe hongey."
3573,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha. Asr ki Namaz ka waqt ho gaya tha, aur log wuzu ka pani talash kar rahe they lekin pani ka kahin pata nahi tha, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (eik bartan ke andar) wuzu ka pani laya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath us bartan mein rakha aur logon se farmaya ke usi pani se wuzu karein. maine dekha ke pani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyon ke nichey se ubal raha tha chunanche logon ne wuzu kya yahan tak ke har shakhs ne wuzu kar liya."
3574,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi safar mein they aur aap ke sath kuchh sahaba kiram bhi they, chaltey chaltey Namaz ka waqt ho gaya to wuzu ke liye kahin pani nahi mila. aakhir jamat mein se aik sahib uthey aur aik badey se pyaley mein thoda sa pani lekar haazire-khidmat huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey liya aur uske pani se wuzu kya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath pyaley par rakha aur farmaya ke aao wuzu karo, poori jamat ne wuzu kya aur tamam aadaab w sunan ke sath poori tarah kar liya. ham tadaad mein 70 ya usi ke lag bhag they."
3575,"Namaz ka waqt ho chuka tha, masjide-Nabawi se jinke ghar qareeb they unhon-ne to wuzu kar liya lekin bahut se log baqi reh gaey. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein patthar ki bani hui aik lagan laai gaee. usmein pani tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath is par rakha lekin uska munh itna tang tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske andar apna hath phaila kar nahi rakh saktey they, chunanche aap ne ungliyan mila lin aur lagan ke andar hath ko daal diya phir (usi pani se) jitney log baqi reh gaey they sab ne wuzu kya. maine puchha ke aap hazraat ki tadaad kya thi? Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke assii aadmi they."
3576,"suleh Hudaibiya ke din logon ko piyaas lagi hui thi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik chhaagal rakha hua tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya baat hai? logon ne kaha ke jo pani aap ke samney hai, us pani ke siwa na to hamarey paas wuzu ke liye koi doosra pani hai aur na peeney ke liye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath chhaagal mein rakh diya aur pani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyon ke darmyan mein se chashmey ki tarah phootney laga aur ham sab logon ne us pani ko piyaa bhi aur us se wuzu bhi kya. maine puchha aap log kitni tadaad mein they? kaha ke agar ham aik laakh bhi hotey to wo pani kafi hota. waisey hamari tadaad us waqt pandarah so thi."
3577,suleh Hudaibiya ke din ham chaudah so ki tadaad mein they. Hudaibiya aik kuwein ka naam hai ham ne us se itna pani kheenchaa ke usmein aik qatra bhi baqi na raha (jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski khabar hui to aap tashrif laaey) aur kuwein ke kinarey baith kar pani ki dua ki aur us pani se kulli ki aur kulli ka pani kuwein mein daal diya. abhi thodi der bhi nahi hui thi ke kunwaan phir pani se bhar gaya. ham bhi us se khub sair huey aur hamarey oont bhi sairaab ho gaey ya pani pi kar lautey.
3578,"abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( meri walida ( Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki awaz suni to aap ki awaz mein bahut kamzori malum hui. mera khayal hai ke aap bahut bhookey hain. kya tumharey paas kuchh khana hai? unhon-ne kaha ji haan, chunanche unhon-ne jau ki chand rotiyaan nikaaliin, phir apni odhnii nikaalii aur usmein rotiyon ko lapet kar mere hath mein chipa diya aur us odhnii ka doosra hissey mere badan par baandh diya. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein mujhey bhejaa. mein jo gaya to aap masjid mein tashrif rakhtey they. aap ke sath bahut se sahaba bhi baithey huey they. main aap ke paas khada ho gaya to aap ne farmaya kya abu-Talha ne tumhen bheja hai? maine arz kya ji haan. aap ne malum farmaya, kuchh khana de kar? maine arz kya ji haan, jo sahaba aap ke sath us waqt maujood they, un sabse aap ne farmaya ke chalo utho, aap tashrif laney lagey aur main aap ke aagey-aagey lapak raha tha aur abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar pahunch kar maine unhein khabar di. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) boley, Umme-Sulaim ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to bahut se logon ko sath laey hain hamarey paas itna khana kahan hai ke sab ko khilaaya ja sakey? Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah aur uske rasool zyada jantey hain (ham fikr kyon karein?) khair abu-Talha aagey badh kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se miley. ab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath wo bhi chal rahe they. Umme-Sulaim ne wahi roti la kar aap ke samney rakh di, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se rotiyon ka chooraa kar diya gaya, Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kuppii nichod kar is par kuchh ghi daal diya, aur is tarah saalan ho gaya, aap ne iske baad is par dua ki jo kuchh bhi Allah Taala ne chaha. phir farmaya das aadmiyon ko bula lo, unhon-ne aisa hi kya, un sab ne roti pet bhar kar khaaii aur jab ye log bahar gaey to aap ne farmaya ke phir das aadmiyon ko bula lo. chunanche das aadmiyon ko bulaya gaya, unhon-ne bhi pet bhar kar khaayaa, jab ye log bahar gaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir das hi aadmiyon ko andar bula lo. unhon-ne aisa hi kya aur unhon-ne bhi pet bhar kar khaayaa. jab wo bahar gaey to aap ne farmaya ke phir das aadmiyon ko dawat de do. is tarah sab logon ne pet bhar kar khana khaayaa. un logon ki tadaad 70 ya 80 thi."
3579,"moa'jazaat ko ham to baaise-barkat samajhtey they aur tum log unse dartey ho. aik martaba ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein they aur pani taqriban khatm ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo kuchh bhi pani bach gaya ho usey talash karo. chunanche log aik bartan mein thoda sa pani laey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath bartan mein daal diya aur farmaya : barkat wala pani lo aur barkat to Allah Taala hi ki taraf se hoti hai, maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyon ke darmyan mein se pani fawwaarey ki tarah phoot raha tha aur ham to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein khaatey waqt khaney ke tasbeeh suntey they."
3580,"unke walid ( Abdullah-bin-Amr bin haraam, jange-Uhud mein) Shahid ho gaey they. aur wo maqrooz they. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur maine arz kya ke mere walid apne uper qarz chhod gaey. idhar mere paas siwa is paidawar ke jo khajooron se hogi aur kuchh nahi hai aur uski paidawar se to barson mein qarz ada nahi ho sakta. isliye aap mere sath tashrif ley chaliye taake qarz-khaah aapko dekh kar zyada munh na phaadein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey (lekin wo nahi maaney ( to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajoor ke jo dher lagey huey they pahley unmein se aik ke charon taraf chaley aur dua ki. isi tarah doosrey dher ke bhii. phir aap is par baith gaey aur farmaya ke khajoorein nikal kar unhein do. chunanche Sara qarz ada ho gaya aur jitni khajoorein qarz mein di thin itni hi bach gain ."
3581,"suffa waley mohtaaj aur ghareeb log they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik martaba farmaya tha ke jiske ghar mein 2 aadmiyon ka khana ho to wo aik teesrey ko bhi apne sath leta jaey aur jiske ghar char aadmiyon ka khana ho wo panchwan aadmi apne sath leta jaey ya chhatey ko bhi ya aap ne isi tarah kuchh farmaya ( rawi ko panch aur chh mein shak hai). khair to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) teen ashabe-Suffa ko apne sath laey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sath das ashaab ko le gaey aur ghar mein, main tha aur mere maan-baap they. abu-Usman ne kaha mujh ko yad nahi Abdur-Rehman ne ye bhi kaha, aur meri aurat aur khaadim jo mere aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) donon ke gharon mein kaam karta tha. lekin khud Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khana khaya aur isha ki Namaz tak wahan thahrey rahe (mahmaanon ko pahley hi bhej chukey they) isliye unhein itna thaharnaa padaa ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khana kha liya. phir Allah Taala ko jitna manzoor tha utnaa hissey raat ka jab guzar gaya to aap ghar wapas aaey. unki biwi ne unse kaha, kya baat hui. aapko apne mehman yad nahi rahe? unhon-ne puchha : kya mahmaanon ko ab tak khana nahi khilaaya ? biwi ne kaha ke mahmaanon ne aap ke aaney tak khaney se inkar kya. unke samney khana pesh kya gaya tha lekin wo nahi maaney . Abdur-Rehman kehtey hain ke main to jaldi se chhup gaya (kyonke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ghussa ho gaey they). aap ne daantaa, aey paa-jii ! aur bahut bura bhala kaha, phir ( mahmaanon se) kaha chalo ab khaao aur khud qism kha li ke main to kabhi na khaaunga. Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Allah ki qasam, phir ham jo luqma bhi (is khaney mein se) uthatey to jaisey nichey se khana aur zyada ho jata tha. sab logon ne pet bhar kar khaya aur khana pahley se bhi zyada bach raha. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo dekha to khana joon ka toon tha ya pahley se bhi zyada. is par unhon-ne apni biwi se kaha, aey banii-faraas ki behan (dekho to ye kya mamla hua) unhon-ne kaha, kuchh bhi nahi, meri aankhon ki thandak ki qasam, khana to pahley se teen guna zyada malum hota hai, phir wo khana Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi khaya aur farmaya ke ye meri wo qism khana to shaitan ki taraf se tha. aik luqma kha kar usey aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein le gaey wahan wo subah tak rakha raha. ittifaq se aik kaafir qaum jiska ham musalmanon se muaahida tha aur muaahide ki muddat khatm ho chuki thi. unse ladney ke liye fauj jama ki gaee. phir ham baara tukdiyaan ho gaey aur har aadmi ke sath kitney aadmi they ye Allah hi janta hai magar itna zaroor malum hai ke aap ne un sardaaron ko lashkar walon ke sath bhejaa. hasil ye ke fauj walon ne usmein se khaayaa. ya Abdur-Rehman ne kuchh aisa hi kahaa."
3582,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein aik saal qahat padaa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Juma ki Namaz ke liye khutba de rahe they ke aik shakhs ne khadey ho kar kaha : ya Rasulullah! ghodey bhook se halaak ho gaey aur bakriyan bhi halaak ho gaiin. aap Allah Taala se dua kijiye ke wo ham par pani barsaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath uthaey aur dua ki. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke us waqt aasman sheeshey ki tarah (bilkul saaf) tha. itney mein hawa chalii. us ne abr (baadal) ko uthaya phir abr ke bahut se tukdey jama ho gaey aur aasman ne maano apne dahaane khol diye. ham jab masjid se nikley to ghar pahunchtey pahunchtey pani mein doob chukey they. barish yun hi doosrey Juma tak barabar hoti rahi. doosrey Juma ko wahi sahib ya koi doosrey phir khadey huey aur arz kya : aey Allah ke rasool! makanon gir gaey. dua farmaiye ke Allah Taala barish ko rok de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraaey aur farmaya : aey Allaah! ab hamarey charon taraf barish barsa (jahaan uski zarurat ho) ham par na barsa. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine jo nazar uthai to dekha ke usi waqt abr phat kar Madina ke ird-gird sarpech ki tarah ho gaya tha.
3583,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik lakdi ka sahara lekar khutba diya kartey they. phir jab member bin gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutbe ke liye is par tashrif ley gaey. is par us lakdi ne baareek awaz se ronaa shuru kar diya. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske qareeb tashrif laey aur apna hath is par phera aur abdul-hameed ne kaha ke hamein Usman bin umr ne khabar di, unhein Muaaz-bin-Alaa ne khabar di aur unhein Naafe ne usi hadis ki aur uski riwayat abu-Aasim ne ki, unse Abu-Rawaad ne, unse Naafe ne aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
3584,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Juma ke din khutbe ke liye aik darakht (ke taney) ke paas khadey hotey ya ( bayan kya ke) khajoor ke darakht ke paas . phir aik Ansari aurat ne ya kisi sahabi ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! kyon na ham aap ke liye aik member taiyaar kar dein ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tumhara ji chahey to kar do. chunanche unhon-ne aap ke liye member taiyaar kar diya. jab Juma ka din hua to aap us member par tashrif ley gaey. is par us khajoor ke taney se bachchey ki tarah roney ki awaz aaney lagi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member se utrey aur usey apne galley se laga liya. jis tarah bachchon ko chup karne ke liye loriyaan detey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi isi tarah usey chup karaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye tanaa isliye ro raha tha ke wo Allah ke us zakar (khas ang) ko suna karta tha jo iske qareeb hota tha.
3585,masjide-Nabawi ki chhat khajoor ke tanon par banai gaee thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab khutbe ke liye tashrif latey to aap unmein se aik taney ke paas khadey ho jatey lekin jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye member bana diya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par tashrif laey. phir ham ne us taney se is tarah ki roney ki awaz suni jaisi b-waqt wilaadat ontni ki awaz hoti hai. aakhir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske qareeb aa kar is par hath rakha to wo chup hua.
3586,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : fitna ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis kis ko yad hai? Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke mujhey zyada yad hai jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha phir bayan karo) mashaAllah ( tum to bahut jari ho. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : insan ki aik aazmaish ( fitna ( to uske ghar, maal aur padaus mein hota hai jiska kaffaara, namaaz, roza, sadqa aur Amr-bil-ma'aroof aur nahii anil-munkar (bhalaaiyon ka hukm dena aur buraaiyon se roknaa) jaisi nekiyan bin jati hain. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main iske mutaalliq nahi poochhtaa, balke meri murad us fitne se hai jo samandar ki tarah (thaathein maartaa) hoga. unhon-ne kaha us fitna ka aap par koi asar nahi padega. aap ke aur us fitne ke darmyan band darwaza hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha wo darwaza khola jaeyga ya todaa jaeyga unhon-ne kaha ke nahi balke tod diya jaeyga umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par farmaya ke phir to band na ho sakega. ham ne Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, kya umr (Raziallahu anhu) us darwazey ke mutaalliq jantey they? unhon-ne farmaya ke isi tarah jantey they jaisey din ke baad raat ke aaney ko har shakhs janta hai. maine aisi hadis bayan ki jo ghalat nahi thi. hamein Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se ( darwaza ke mutaalliq ( poochhtey huey dar malum hua. isliye ham ne Masruq se kaha to unhon-ne puchha ke wo darwaza kon hain? to unhon-ne bataya ke wo khud umr (Raziallahu anhu) hi hain."
3587,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak nahi qaaim hogi jab tak tum aik aisi qaum ke sath jang na kar lo jinke jootey baal ke hon aur jab tak tum turkon se jang na kar lo, jinki aankhen chhoti hongii, chehrey surkh hongey, naak chhoti aur chaptii hogi, chehrey aisey hongey jaisey teh-b-teh dhaal hoti hai.''"
3588,"aur tum hukumat ke liye sabse zyada behtar shakhs usey paogey jo hukumat karne ko bura janey (yani us mansab ko khud ke liye na-pasand karey) yahan tak ke wo usmein phans jaey. logon ki misal kaan ki si hai jo jahiliyat mein sharif they, wo Islam laney ke baad bhi sharif hain."
3589,aur tum par aik aisa daur bhi aaney wala hai ke tum mein se koi apne sarey gharbaar aur maal w daulat se badh kar mujh ko dekh lena zyada pasand karega.
3590,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim na hogi jab tak ke tum Iraaniyon ke Shahar khauz aur kirmaan walon se jang na kar logey. chehrey unke surkh hongey. naak chaptii hogi. aankhen chhoti hongi aur chehrey aisey hongey jaisey teh-b-teh dhaal hoti hai aur unke jootey baalon waley hongey. Yahya ke ilawa us hadis ko auron ne bhi Abdur-Razzaq se riwayat kya hai.
3591,"ham Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhon-ne kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat mein teen saal raha hun, apni poori umr mein mujhey hadis yad karne ka itna shauq kabhi nahi hua jitna in teen saalon mein tha. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey suna, aap ne apne hath se yun ishara karke farmaya ke qiyamat ke qareeb tum log (muslmaan) aik aisi qaum se jang karogey jinke jootey baalon ke hongey ( murad yahi Iraanii hain) Sufiyan ne aik martaba ( وهو هذا البارز (ke bajaey alfaz ( وهم أهل البازر‏ ( naql kiye (yani Iraanii , ya kurdii , ya Delam waley log murad hain) ."
3592,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke qareeb tum aik aisi qaum se jang karogey jo baalon ka jootaa pahantii hogi aur aik aisi qaum se jang karogey jinke munh teh-b-teh dhaalon ki tarah hongey."
3593,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna tha ke tum yahudiyon se aik jang karogey aur is mein un par ghalib aa jaogey. us waqt ye kaifiyat hogi ke (agar koi Yahudi jaan bachaney ke liye kisi pahaad mein bhi chhup jaeyga to) patthar bolega ke aey muslmaan! ye Yahudi meri aad mein chipa hua hai, usey qatl kar de."
3594,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''logon par aik aisa zamana aayega ke jihad ke liye fauj jama hogi, puchha jaeyga ke fauj mein koi aisey buzurg bhi hain jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat uthai ho? unse kaha jaeyga ke yahan hain to unke zariey fateh ki dua mangi jaeygi. phir aik jihad hoga aur puchha jaeyga : kya fauj mein koi aisey shakhs hain jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kisi sahabi ki sohbat uthai ho? unse kaha jaeyga ke yahan hain to unke zariey fateh ki dua mangi jaeyga phir unki dua ki barkat se fateh hogi."
3595,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke aik sahib aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se faqr w faaqa ki shikayat ki, phir doosrey sahib aaey aur raston ki bd-amnii ki shikayat ki, is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : adii! tum ne maqam Haira dekha hai? (jo Kufa ke paas aik basti hai) maine arz kya ke maine dekha to nahi, albatta uska naam maine suna hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tumhari zindagi kuchh aur lambi hui to tum dekhogey ke hodaj mein aik aurat akelii Haira se safar karegi aur (Makka pahunch kar) Kaba ka tawaaf karegi aur Allah ke siwa usey kisi ka bhi khof na hoga. maine (hairat se) apne dil mein kaha, phir qabila tay ke un daakuon ka kya hoga jinhoney shehron ko tabah kar diya hai aur fasaad ki aag sulgaa rakhi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum kuchh aur dinon tak zinda rahe to Kisraa ke khazaaney (tum par) kholey jaengey. main (hairat mein) bol padaa Kisraa bin Hurmuz ( Iraan ka badshah ( Kisraa ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan Kisraa bin Hurmuz ! aur agar tum kuchh dinon tak aur zinda rahe to ye bhi dekhogey ke aik shakhs apne hath mein sona chandi bhar kar niklega , usey kisi aisey aadmi ki talash hogi (jo uski zakat ( qabool kar ley lekin usey koi aisa aadmi nahi milega jo usey qabool kar ley. Allah Taala se mulaqat ka jo din muqarrar hai us waqt tum mein se har koi Allah se us haal mein mulaqat karega ke darmyan mein koi tarjuman na hoga (balke parwardigar us se bilaa-waasta baatein karega) Allah Taala us se malum karega. kya maine tumharey paas rasool nahi bhejey they jinhoney tum tak mera paigham pahuncha diya ho? wo arz karega beshak tu ney bheja tha. Allah Taala malum farmaeyga kya maine maal aur aulad tumhen nahi di thi? kya maine unke zariey tumhen fazeelat nahi di thi? wo jawab dega beshak tu ney diya tha. phir wo apni dahini taraf dekhega to siwa jahannam ke usey aur kuchh nazar na aayega phir wo baain taraf dekhega to idhar bhi jahannam ke siwa aur kuchh nazar nahi aayega. Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they ke jahannam se daro, agarche khajoor ke aik tukdey ke zariey ho. agar kisi ko khajoor ka aik tukda bhi muyassar na aa sakey to (kisi se) aik achchha kalima hi keh de. Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine hodaj mein baithi hui aik akelii aurat ko to khud dekh liya ke Haira se safar ke liye nikli aur (Makka pahunch kar) us ne Kaba ka tawaaf kya aur usey Allah ke siwa aur kisi se (daaku wghaira) ka (raastey mein) khof nahi tha aur mujaahideen ki us jamat main to main khud Sharik tha jisne Kisraa bin Hurmuz ke khazaaney fateh kiye aur agar tum log kuchh dinon aur zinda rahe to wo bhi dekh logey jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik shakhs apne hath main ( zakat ka sona chandi ( bhar kar niklega ( lekin usey leney wala koi nahi milega ( mujh se Abdullah-bin Muhammad ne bayan kya, kaha ham se abu-Aasim ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko Sa'daan-bin-Bashr ne khabar di, unse Abu-Mujaahid ne bayan kya, unse Mahal-bin-Khaleefa ne bayan kya, aur unhon-ne Adi (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha, phir yahi hadis naql ki jo uper zikr hui hai."
3596,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din Madina se bahar nikley aur shohdaae-Uhad par Namaz padhi jaisey maiyat par padhtey hain. uske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif laey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main (hauze-kausar par) tum se pahley Pohnchoonga aur qiyamat ke din tumharey liye meere-saamaan banoonga. main tum par gawahi doonga aur Allah ki qism main apne hauze-kausar ko us waqt bhi dekh raha hun, mujhey poori zameen ke khazaanon ki kunjiyaan di gaee hain aur qism Allah ki mujhey tumharey barey mein ye khof nahi ke tum shirk karne lagogey. main to is se darta hun ke kahin duniya daari mein pad kar aik doosrey se rashk w hasad na karne lago."
3597,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik martaba Madina ke aik buland teele par chadhey aur farmaya ''jo kuchh main dekh raha hun kya tumhen bhi nazar aa raha hai? main fitnon ko dekh raha hun ke tumharey gharon mein wo is tarah gir rahe hain jaisey barish ki boondein gira kartii hain.''
3598,"ham ko Zainab-bint-abii-Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke ghar tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut pareshan nazar aa rahe they aur ye farma rahe they ke Allah Taala ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi, Arab ke liye tabahi us shar se aaeygii jiske waaqe honey ka zamana qareeb aa gaya hai. aaj yaajooj maajooj ki diwar mein itna shigaaf paida ho gaya hai aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ungliyon se halqa bana kar uski wazaahat ki. Ummul-Momenin Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! ham mein nek log hongey phir bhi ham halaak kar diye jaaeinge? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, jab khabaasatein badh jaeyngi (to aisa hoga)."
3599,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey to farmaya ''sub'haan-Allaah ! kaisey kaisey khazaaney utrey hain (jo musalmanon ko milengey) aur kya-kya fitney w fasaad utrey hain.''
3600,"mein dekh raha hun ke tumhen bakriyon se bahut mohabbat hai aur tum unhein paaltey ho to tum unki nigahdaasht achi kya karo aur unki naak ki safaaii ka bhi khayal rakha karo. kyonke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke logon par aisa zamana aayega ke musalman ka sabse umda maal uski bakriyan hongi jinhein lekar wo pahaad ki chotiyon par chadh jaeyga ya (aap ne ( سعف الجبال (ke lafz farmaai ( wo barish girney ki jagah mein chala jaeyga is tarah wo apne Deen ko fitnon se bachaney ke liye bhaagta phirega."
3601,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''fitnon ka daur jab aayega to usmein baithney wala khada rehney waley se behtar hoga, khada rehney wala chalney waley se behtar hoga aur chalney wala daudney waley se behtar hoga jo usmein jhaankega fitna bhi usey uchak lega aur us waqt jisey jahan bhi panah mil jaey bas wahin panah pakad ley taake apne Deen ko fitnon se bacha sakey. ''"
3602,namazon mein aik Namaz aisi hai ke jis se wo chhoot jaey maano uska gharbaar sab barbad ho gaey. (aur wo Asr ki Namaz hai).
3603,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' mere baad tum par aik aisa zamana aayega jis main tum par dusron ko muqaddam kya jaeyga aur aisi baatein samney aaengii jinko tum bura samjho gey.'' logon ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! us waqt hamein aap kya hukm farmatey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo huquq tum par dusron ke wajib hon unhein ada kartey rehna aur apne huquq Allah hi se maangnaa. (yani sabr karna aur apna haq leney ke liye khaleefa aur Hakim waqt se baghaawat na karnaa).
3604,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''is qabeele Quraish ke kuchh aadmi logon ko halaak w barbad kar dengey.'' sahaba ne arz kya : aisey waqt ke liye aap hamein kya hukm farmatey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kaash log unse bas alag hi rehtey. '' Mehmood-bin Ghelaan ne bayan kya ke ham se Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko Shoba ne khabar di, unhein Abu-Tayyah ne, unhon-ne Abu-Zaraa se suna."
3605,"mein Marwaan-bin-Hakam aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha. us waqt maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha ke maine sachchon ke sachey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke meri ummat ki barbadi Quraish ke chand ladkon ke hathon par hogi. Marwan ne puchha : naujawaan ladkon ke hath par? is par Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar tum chaho to main unke naam bhi ley dun ke wo bani falan aur bani falan hongey."
3606,"doosrey sahaba kiram to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khair ke mutaalliq sawal kya kartey they lekin main shar ke barey mein poochhta tha us khof se ke kahin mein unmein na phans jaun. to maine aik martaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham jahiliyat aur shar ke zamaney mein they. phir Allah Taala ne hamein ye khair w barkat (Islam ki) ata farmai, ab kya is khair ke baad phir shar ka koi zamana aayega? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, maine sawal kya, aur us shar ke baad phir khair ka koi zamana aayega ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, lekin us khair par kuchh dhuaan hoga. maine arz kya wo dhuaan kya hoga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab diya ke aisey log paida hongey jo meri sunnat aur tareeqey ke ilawa doosrey tareeqey ikhtiyar karengey. unmein koi baat achi hogi koi burii. maine sawal kya : kya us khair ke baad phir shar ka koi zamana aayega? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, jahannam ke darwazon ki taraf bulaney waley paida hongey, jo unki baat qabool karega usey wo jahannam mein jhonk dengey. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! unke ausaaf bhi bayan farma dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo log hamari hi qaum w mazhab ke hongey. hamari hi zaban bolengey . maine arz kya, phir agar main un logon ka zamana paon to mere liye aap ka hukm kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke musalmanon ki jamat aur unke imam ko lazim pakadnaa, maine arz kya agar musalmanon ki koi jamat na ho aur na unka koi imam ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir un tamam firqon se apne ko alag rakhna. agarche tujhey uske liye kisi darakht ki jad chabaanii padey, yahan tak ke teri maut aa jaey aur to usi haalat par ho (to ye terey haq mein unki sohbat mein rehney se behtar hoga)."
3607,mere sathiyon ne (yani sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne) to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhalai ke halaat seekhey aur maine burai ke halaat malum kiye.
3608,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim nahi hogi jab tak 2 jamatein (musalmanon ki) aapas mein jang na kar lein aur donon ka dawa aik hoga (ke wo haq par hain).''
3609,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim na hogi jab tak 2 jamatein aapas mein jang na kar lein. donon mein badi bhari jang hogi. halanke donon ka dawa aik hi hoga aur qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim na hogi jab tak taqriban tees jhootey dajjal paida na ho lein. unmein har aik ka yahi guman hoga ke wo Allah ka Nabi hai.''
3610,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein maujood they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( jange-Hunain ka maale-ghanimat ( taqseem farma rahe they itney mein bani Tameem ka aik shakhs zul-khuwesra naam ke aaya aur kehney laga ke ya Rasulullah ! insaf se kaam lijiye . ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' afsos ! agar main hi insaf na karun to duniya mein phir kon insaf karega . agar main zaalim ho jaun tab to meri bhi tabahi aur barbadi ho jaaey.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! iske barey mein mujhey ijazat dein mein uski gardan mar dun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey chhod do. iske jod ke kuchh log paida hongey ke tum apne rozon ko unke rozon ke muqabil naacheez samjhogey. wo Quran ki tilawat karengey lekin wo unke halaq ke nichey nahi utreyga. ye log Deen se isi tarah nikal jaeinge jaisey zor daar teer janwar se paar ho jata hai. us teer ke phal ko agar dekha jaey to usmein koi cheez (khoon wghaira) nazar na aaeygii phir iske patthey ko agar dekha jaey to chhid mein uske phal ke dakhil honey ki jagah se uper jo lagaya jata hai to wahan bhi kuchh na milega. iske nazii (nazii teer mein lagai janey wali lakdi ko kehtey hain) ko dekha jaey to wahan bhi kuchh nishan nahi milega. isi tarah agar uske par ko dekha jaey to usmein bhi kuchh nahi milega. halanke gandagi aur khoon se wo teer guzra hai. unki alamat aik kala shakhs hoga. uska aik bazu aurat ke pistaan ki tarah (uthaa hua) hoga ya gosht ke lothdey ki tarah hoga aur harkat kar raha hoga. ye log musalmanon ke behtreen giroh se baghaawat karengey. Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke maine ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi aur main gawahi deta hun ke Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse jang ki thi (yani khawaarij se) us waqt main bhi Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha aur unhon-ne us shakhs ko talash karaya (jisey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us giroh ki alamat ke taur par batlaya tha) aakhir wo laya gaya. maine usey dekha to uska pura huliya bilkul Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bayan ki hui khoobiyon ke mutabiq tha.
3611,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, jab tum se koi baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hawale se main bayan karun to ye samjho ke mere liye aasman se gir jana us se behtar hai ke main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par koi jhoot baandhoon albatta jab main apni taraf se koi baat tum se kahun to ladai to tadbeer aur faraib hi ka naam hai (us mein koi baat bana kar kahun to mumkin hai). dekho maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke aakhir zamane mein kuchh log aisey paida hongey jo chhotey-chhotey daanton waale, kam aql aur bewaqoof hongey. baatein wo kahengey jo duniya ki behtreen baat hogi. lekin Islam se is tarah saaf nikal chukey hongey jaisey teer janwar ke paar nikal jata hai. unka eman unke halaq se nichey nahi utrega, tum unhein jahan bhi paogey qatl kar do, kyonke unke qatl se qaatil ko qiyamat ke din sawab milega."
3612,ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shikayat ki. aap us waqt apni aik chadar par tek diye Kaba ke saaey mein baithey huey they. ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein arz kya ke aap hamarey liye madad kyon nahi talab farmatey. hamarey liye Allah se dua kyon nahi maangtey ( ham kaafiron ki eiizaa dahii se tang aa chukey hain) . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' (eman laney ki saza mein) tum se pehli ummaton ke logon ke liye garhaa khodaa jata aur unhein usmein daal diya jata. phir unke sar par aaraa rakh kar unke 2 tukdey kar diye jatey phir bhi wo apne Deen se na phirtey. lohey ke kanghey unke gosht mein dhansaa kar unki haddiyon aur putthon par pherey jatey phir bhi wo apna eman na chhodtey. Allah ki qism ye Amr (Islam) bhi kamaal ko pahunchega aur aik zamana aayega ke aik sawar maqam san'aa se Hazare-maut tak safar karega ( lekin raston ke pur-amn honey ki wjah se usey Allah ke siwa aur kisi ka dar nahi hoga. ya sirf bhediye ka khof hoga ke kahin uski bakriyon ko na kha jaey lekin tum log jaldi kartey ho.
3613,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik din Saabit-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) nahi miley to aik sahabi ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! main aap ke liye unki khabar laataa hun. chunanche wo unke yahan aaey to dekha ke apne ghar mein sar jhukaaey baithey hain, unhon-ne puchha ke kya haal hai? unhon-ne kaha ke bura haal hai. unki aadat thi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bhi unchi awaz mein bola kartey they. unhon-ne kaha usi liye mera amal ghaarat ho gaya aur main dozkhiyon mein ho gaya hun. wo sahabi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko itlaa di ke Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) yun keh rahe hain. Musa bin Anas ne bayan kya, lekin dusri martaba wahi sahabi Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aik badi khushkhabri lekar wapas huey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya tha ke Sabit ke paas jao aur us se kaho ke wo ahale-jahannam mein se nahi hain balke wo ahle-jannat mein se hain."
3614,"aik sahabi ( Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu)) ne (namaz mein) sura Kahaf ki tilawat ki. usi ghar mein ghoda bandhaa hua tha, ghodey ne uchhalnaa koodnaa shuru kar diya. ( Usaid ne idhar khayal na kya usko Allah ke sipurd kya ( iske baad jab unhon-ne salam phera to dekha ke badal ke aik tukdey ne unke sarey ghar par saaya kar rakha hai. is waqia ka zikr unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Quran padhta hi reh kyonke ye ( سكينة ( hai jo Quran ki wjah se nazil hui ya (iske bajaey rawi ne) (تنزلت للقرآن (ke alfaz kahey."
3615,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) mere walid ke paas unke ghar aaey aur unse aik paalaan khareedaa. phir unhon-ne mere walid se kaha ke apne betey ke zariey usey mere sath bhej do. Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya chunanche main us kajaawey ko utha kar aap ke sath chala aur mere walid uski qeemat ke rupye parakhwaaney lagey. mere walid ne unse puchha aey Abu-Bakar ! mujhey wo waqia sunaaiye jab aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ghaare-saur se hijrat ki thi to aap donon ne wo waqt kaisey guzara tha? is par unhon-ne bayan kya ke ji haan, raat bhar to ham chaltey rahe aur doosrey din subah ko bhi lekin jab do-pahar ka waqt hua aur rasta bilkul sunsaan pad gaya ke koi bhi aadmi guzarta hua dikhai nahi deta tha to hamein aik lambi chattaan dikhai di, iske saaey mein dhoop nahi thi. ham wahan utar gaey aur maine khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik jagah apne hath se theek kar di aur aik chadar wahan bichhaa di. phir maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! aap yahan aaraam farmaein main nigrani karunga, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey aur main charon taraf halaat dekhney ke liye niklaa. ittifaq se mujhey aik charwaha mila. wo bhi apni bakriyon ke rewad ko usi chattaan ke saaey mein lana chahta tha jiske taley maine wahan padao daala tha. wahi uska bhi irada tha, maine us se puchha ke to kis qabeeley se hai? us ne bataya ke Madina ya (raawii ne kaha ke) Makka ke falan shakhs se, maine us se puchha ke kya teri bakriyon se doodh mil sakta hai? usne kaha ke haan. maine puchha kya hamarey liye to doodh nikal sakta hai? usne kaha ke haan. chunanche wo aik bakri pakad ke laya. maine us se kaha ke pahley than ko mittii, baal aur dusri gandagiyon se saaf kar ley. Abu-Ishaq rawi ne kaha ke maine Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke unhon-ne apne aik hath ko doosrey par mar kar than ko jhadney ki sura bayan ki. us ne lakdi ke aik pyaley mein doodh nikaalaa. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik bartan apne sath rakh liya tha. aap us se pani piyaa kartey they aur wuzu bhi kar letey they. phir main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya (aap so rahe they) mein aapko jagaanaa pasand nahi karta tha. lekin baad mein jab main aaya to aap bedaar ho chukey they. maine pahley doodh ke bartan par pani bahaya jab uske nichey ka hissa thanda ho gaya to maine arz kya : aey Allah ke rasool! doodh pi liijiye, unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne doodh nosh farmaya jis se mujhey khushi hasil hui. phir aap ne farmaya kya abhi kooch karne ka waqt nahi aaya? maine arz kya ke aa gaya hai. unhon-ne kaha : jab suraj dhal gaya to ham ne kooch kya. baad mein Suraaqa-bin-Maalik hamara peechhaa karta hua yahin pahuncha. maine kaha : ya Rasulullah! ab to ye hamarey qareeb hi pahunch gaya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke gham na karo. Allah hamarey sath hai. aap ne phir uske liye baddua ki aur uska ghoda usey liye huey pet tak zameen mein dhans gaya. mera khayal hai ke zameen badi sakht thi. ye shak ( rawi hadis) Zuhair ko tha. Suraqa ne kaha : main samajhta hun ke aap logon ne mere liye baddua ki hai. agar ab aap log mere liye (is museebat se nijat ki) dua kar dein to Allah ki qism main aap logon ki talash mein aaney waley tamam logon ko wapas lota doonga. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir dua ki to wo nijat pa gaya. phir to jo bhi usey rastey mein milta us se wo kehta tha ke main bahut talash kar chuka hun. qatae taur par wo idhar nahi hain. is tarah jo bhi milta usey wo wapas apne sath ley jata Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke usne hamarey sath jo wada kya tha usey pura kya."
3616,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik dehati ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif ley gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bhi kisi mareez ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif ley jatey to farmatey koi harj nahi, inshaAllah ye bukhar gunahon ko dho dega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us dehati se bhi yahi farmaya ke koi harj nahi inshaAllah (ye bukhaar) gunahon ko dho dega. us ne is par kaha : aap kehtey hain gunahon ko dhoney wala hai. hargiz nahi. ye to bahut hi zyada shadeed qism ka bukhar hai ya (raawii ne) ( تثور ( kaha ( donon ka mafhoom aik hi hai) ke bukhar aik boodhey khoosat par josh mar raha hai jo qabr ki ziyaarat kiraaey baghair nahi chhodega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha to phir yun hi hoga."
3617,aik shakhs pahley Esai tha. phir wo Islam mein dakhil ho gaya tha. us ne sura al-Baqara aur Aale-Imran padh li thi aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka munshi bin gaya lekin phir wo shakhs murtad ho kar Esai ho gaya aur kehney laga ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye jo kuchh maine likh diya hai iske siwa unhein aur kuchh bhi malum nahi. phir Allah Taala ke hukm se uski maut waaqe ho gaee aur uske aadmiyon ne usey dafn kar diya. jab subah hui to unhon-ne dekha ke uski laash qabr se nikal kar zameen ke uper padi hai. Esai logon ne kaha ke ye Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur uske sathiyon ka kaam hai. chunkey unka Deen us ne chhod diya tha isliye unhon-ne uski qabr khodi hai aur laash ko bahar nikal kar phenk diya hai. chunanche dusri qabr unhon-ne khodi jo bahut zyada gehri thi. lekin jab subah hui to phir laash bahar thi. is martaba bhi unhon-ne yahi kaha ke ye Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur unke sathiyon ka kaam hai chunkey unka Deen us ne chhod diya tha isliye uski qabr khod kar unhon-ne laash bahar phenk di hai. phir unhon-ne qabr khodi aur jitni gehri unke bas mein thi karke usey uske andar daal diya lekin subah hui to phir laash bahar thi. ab unhein yaqin aaya ke ye kisi insan ka kaam nahi hai) balke ye maiyat Allah Taala ke azab mein giraftaar hai) chunanche unhon-ne usey yoonhii (zameen par) daal diya.
3618,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab Kisraa (shaahए-Iraan) halaak ho jaeyga to phir koi Kisraa paida nahi hoga aur us zaat ki qism jiske qabze mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai tum unke khazaaney Allah ke rastey mein zaroor kharch karogey.''
3619,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab Kisraa halaak hoga to uske baad koi Kisraa paida nahi hoga aur jab qaisar halaak hoga to koi qaisar phir paida nahi hoga ''aur rawi ne (pahlii hadis ki tarah is hadis ko bhi bayan kya aur) kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum un donon ke khazaaney Allah ke rastey mein kharch karogey. ''
3620,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein Musailma kazzaab Madina mein aaya aur ye kehney laga ke agar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ''Amr'' (yani khilaafat) ko apne baad mujhey saunp dein to main unki ittaba (pairvi) ke liye taiyaar hun. Musailma apne bahut se mureedon ko sath lekar Madina aaya tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske paas (usey samjhaaney ke liye) tashrif ley gaey. aap ke sath Saabit-bin-Qais-bin Shamas (Raziallahu anhu) they aur aap ke hath mein khajoor ki aik chhadi thi. aap wahan thahar gaey jahan Musailma apne aadmiyon ke sath maujood tha. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya agar to mujh se chhadi bhi maangey to main tujhey nahi de sakta (khilaafat to badi cheez hai) aur parwardigar ki marzii ko to taal nahi sakta agar to Islam se peeth pherega to Allah tujh ko tabah kar dega aur main samajhta hun ke to wahi hai jo mujhey (khuwaab mein) dikhaya gaya tha.
3621,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ''main soyaa hua tha ke maine ( khuwab mein) soney ke 2 kangan apne hathon mein dekhey. mujhey us khuwab se bahut fikr hui, phir khuwab mein hi wahi ke zariey mujhey batlaya gaya ke main un par phoonk maarun . chunanche jab maine phoonk maari to wo donon ud gaey. maine us se ye tabeer li ke mere baad jhootey Nabi hongey.'' to unmein se aik to Aswad ansaa hai aur doosra Yamaama ka Musailma kazzaab tha."
3622,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''maine khuwab mein dekha tha ke main Makka se aik aisi zameen ki taraf hijrat kar raha hun jahan khajoor ke baghaat hain. is par mera zahan idhar gaya ke ye maqam yamaama ya hijr hoga. lekin wo yasrib Madina Munawra hai aur usi khuwab mein maine dekha ke maine talwaar hilaaii to wo beech mein se toot gaee. ye us museebat ki taraf ishara tha jo Uhud ki ladai mein musalmanon ko uthaanii padi thi. phir maine dusri martaba usey hilaayaa to wo pahley se bhi achi sura mein ho gaee. ye us waaqie ki taraf ishara tha ke Allah Taala ne Makka ki fateh di aur musalman sab ikatthey ho gaey. maine usi khuwab mein gaaein dekhein aur Allah Taala ka jo kaam hai wo behtar hai. un gaayon se un musalmanon ki taraf ishara tha jo Uhud ki ladai mein Shahid kiye gaey aur khair w bhalai wo thi jo hamein Allah Taala ne khair w sachchai ka badla badr ki ladai ke baad ata farmaya tha.''
3623,"Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aaiin, unki chaal main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki chaal se badi mushabihat (similarity) thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : beti aao marhabaa! iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein apni daain taraf ya baain taraf bithaayaa, phir unke kaan mein aap ne chupkey se koi baat kahi to wo roney lagiin, maine unse kaha ke aap roti kyon ho? phir dobara Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke kaan mein kuchh kaha to wo hans din. maine unse kaha aaj gham ke fauran baad hi khushi ki jo kaifiyat maine aap ke chehrey par dekhi wo pahley kabhi nahi dekhi thi. phir maine unse puchha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaya tha? unhon-ne kaha jab tak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zinda hain mein aap ke raaz ko kisi par nahi khol saktii. chunanche maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad poochha."
3624,"to unhon-ne bataya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere kaan mein kaha tha ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) har saal Quran Majeed ka aik door kya kartey they, lekin us saal unhon-ne 2 martaba door kya hai, mujhey yaqin hai ke ab meri maut qareeb hai aur mere gharaaney mein sabse pahley mujh se aa milney wali tum hogi. mein (aap ki us khabar par) roney lagi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum is par razi nahi ke jannat ki aurton ki sardaar banegii ya (aap ne farmaya ke) momina aurton ki, to is par main hansi thi."
3625,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne marz ke zamane main apni beti Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko bulaya aur chupkey se koi baat unse farmai to wo roney lagiin. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bulaya aur chupkey se phir koi baat farmai to wo hansiin. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir maine Fatima (Raziallahu anha) se iske mutaalliq poochha.
3626,"to unhon-ne bataya ke pehli martaba jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se aahista se guftgu ki thi to usmein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke aap ki is marz mein wafat ho jaeygi jis mein waqei aap ki wafat hui. main is par ro padii. phir dobara Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aahista se mujh se jo baat kahi usmein aap ne farmaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahale-bait mein, main sabse pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ja miloongii. main is par hansi thi."
3627,umr bin-Khattab Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne paas bithatey they. is par Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se shikayat ki ke un jaisey to hamarey ladkey bhi hain. lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke ye mahz unke ilm ki wjah se hai. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aayat (إذا جاء نصر الله والفتح‏) ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne jawab diya ke ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat thi jiski khabar Allah Taala ne aapko di umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya jo tum ne samjha hai main bhi wahi samajhta hun.
3628,"maut ke marz main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laaey, aap aik chikney kapdey se sar Mubarak par patti baandhey huey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjide-Nabawi mein member par tashrif farma huey phir jaisey honii chahiye Allah Taala ki hamd w sana ki, phir farmaya : ammaa ba'd! : (aaney waley daur mein) doosrey logon ki tadaad bahut badh jaeygi lekin Ansar kam hotey jaaenge aur aik zamana aayega ke dusron ke muqaabley mein unki tadaad itni kam ho jaeygi jaisey khaney mein namak hota hai. isliye agar tum mein se koi shakhs kahin ka Hakim baney aur apni hukumat ki wjah se wo kisi ko nuqsan aur nafa bhi pahuncha sakta ho to usey chahiye ke Ansar ke nekon (ki nekiyon) ko qabool karey aur jo burey hon unse darguzar kar diya kare. ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aakhiri majlise-wa'z thi."
3629,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ko aik din sath lekar bahar tashrif laey aur member par unko lekar chadh gaey phir farmaya ''meraa ye betaa saiyed hai aur ummeed hai ke Allah Taala iske zariey musalmanon ki 2 jamaton mein milaap kara dega.''
3630,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ja'far-bin-abii-Taalib aur Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ki khabar pahley hi sahaba ko suna di thi, us waqt aap ki aankhon se aansu jari they."
3631,"(unki shadi ke mauqe par) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya kya tumharey paas qaaleen hain? maine arz kya, hamarey paas qaaleen kahan ? (ham ghareeb log hain) is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''yaad rakho aik waqt aayega ke tumharey paas umda-umda qaaleen hongey.'' ab jab main us se (apni biwi se) kehta hun ke apne qaaleen hata ley to wo kehti hai ke kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tum se nahi farmaya tha ke aik waqt aayega jab tumharey paas qaaleen hongey. chunanche main unhein wahin rehney deta hun (aur chup ho jata hun) ."
3632,"Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) Umra ki niyat se (Makka) aaey aur abu-Safwaan Umayya-bin-Khalaf ke yahan utrey. Umayya bhi Sham (Syria) jatey huey (tijaarat wghaira ke liye) jab Madina se guzarta to Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan qiyam kya karta tha. Umayya ne Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : abhi thehro, jab do-pahar ka waqt ho jaey aur log ghaafil ho jayen (tab tawaaf karna kyonke Makka ke mushrik musalmanon ke dushman they) Sad (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, chunanche maine ja kar tawaaf shuru kar diya. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) abhi tawaaf kar hi rahe they ke abu-Jahal aa gaya aur kehney laga, ye Kaba ka tawaaf kon kar raha hai? Sad (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke main Sad hun. abu-Jahal bola : tum Kaba ka tawaaf khub amn se kar rahe ho halanke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur uske sathiyon ko panah de rakhi hai. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : haan theek hai. is tarah donon mein baat badh gaee. phir Umayya ne Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : abul-Hakam ( abu-Jahal (ke samney unchi awaz se na bolo. wo is wadi (Makka) ka sardaar hai. is par Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qism agar tum ne mujhey Baitullah ke tawaaf se rokaa to main bhi tumhari Sham (Syria) ki tijarat khaak mein mila doonga (kyonke Sham (Syria) janey ka sirf aik hi rasta hai jo Madina se jata hai) bayan kya ke Umayya barabar Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se yahi kehta raha ke apni awaz buland na karo aur unhein (muqaabla se) roktaa raha. aakhir Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ko is par ghussa aa gaya aur unhon-ne Umayya se kaha, chal parey hat maine Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se terey mutaalliq suna hai. aap ne farmaya tha ke tujh ko abu-Jahal hi qatl karaaega . Umayya ne puchha : mujhey? Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : haan tujh ko. tab to Umayya kehney laga. Allah ki qism Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab koi baat kehtey hain to wo ghalat nahi hoti phir wo apni biwi ke paas aaya aur us ne us se kaha tumhen malum nahi, mere Yasrabii bhai ne mujhey kya baat batai hai? us ne puchha : unhon-ne kya kaha ? Umayya ne bataya ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) keh chukey hain ke abu-Jahal mujh ko qatl karaaega. wo kehney lagi Allah ki qism Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghalat baat zaban se nahi nikaaltey. phir aisa hua ke ahale-Makka badr ki ladai ke liye rawaana honey lagey aur Umayya ko bhi bulaney wala aaya to Umayya se uski biwi ne kaha, tumhen yad nahi raha tumhara Yasribii bhai tumhen kya khabar de gaya tha. bayan kya ke us yad dihaanii par Umayya ne chaha ke is jang mein shirkat na kare. lekin abu-Jahal ne kaha : tum wadi Makka ke raees ho. isliye kam se kam aik ya 2 din ke liye hi tumhen chalnaa padega. is tarah wo unke sath jang mein shirkat ke liye nikla aur Allah Taala ne usko qatl kara diya."
3633,"mujhey ye baat malum karaai gaee ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aik martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur aap se baatein kartey rahe. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Ummul-Momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) baithi hui thin. jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) chaley gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Umme-Salma se farmaya : malum hai ye kon sahib they? ya aisey hi alfaz irshad farmaaey. abu-Usman ne bayan kya ke Umme-Salma ne jawab diya ke ye Dahiya Kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) they. Umme-Salma ne bayan kya Allah ki qism main samjhey baithi thi ke wo Dahiya Kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) hain. aakhir jab maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khutba suna jis mein aap Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) (ke aaney) ki khabar de rahe they, to main samjhii ke wo Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) hi they. ya aisey hi alfaz kahey. bayan kya ke maine abu-Usman se puchha ke aap ne ye hadis kis se sunii? to unhon-ne bataya ke Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se suni hai."
3634,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''maine (khuwaab mein) dekha ke log aik maidan mein jama ho rahe hain. unmein se Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur aik kuwein se unhon-ne aik ya 2 dol pani bhar kar nikaalaa, pani nikalney mein unmein kuchh kamzori malum hoti thi aur Allah unko bakhshey. phir wo dol umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne sanbhaalaa. unke hath mein jatey hi wo aik bada dol ho gaya maine logon mein un jaisa taaqatwar pahlwaan aur bahaadur insan unki tarah kaam karne wala nahi dekha (unhon-ne itney dol kheenchey)  ke log apne oonton ko bhi pilaa pilaa kar unke thikaanon mein le gaey aur Hammam ne bayan kya ke maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke waastey se bayan kar rahe they ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne 2 dol kheenchey."
3635,"yahood , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aapko bataya ke unke yahan aik mard aur aik aurat ne zina kya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke rajm (sangsaar) ke barey mein Taurait mein kya hukm hai? wo boley ye ke ham unhein ruswa karein aur unhein kode lagaey jaaein. is par Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum log jhootey ho. Taurait mein rajm (sangsaar) ka hukm maujood hai. Taurait laao. phir Yahudi Taurait laey aur usey khola . lekin rajm (sangsaar) se mutaalliq jo aayat thi usey aik Yahudi ne apne hath se chipa liya aur us se pahley aur uske baad ki ibaarat padhney laga. Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke zara apna hath to uthao jab us ne hath uthaya to wahan aayat rajm (sangsaar) maujood thi. ab wo sab kehney lagey ke aey Muhammad! Abdullaah-bin-Salaam ne sach kaha, beshak Taurait mein rajm (sangsaar) ki aayat maujood hai. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se un donon ko rajm (sangsaar) kya gaya. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine rajm (sangsaar) ke waqt dekha. Yahudi mard us aurat par jhukaa padta tha. usko pattharon ki mar se bachaataa tha."
3636,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein chaand ke phat kar do tukdey ho gaey they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke logo is par gawah rehna.
3637,Makka walon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha tha ke unhein koi moa'jza dikhaaiin to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shaqe-Qamar ka moa'jza yani chaand ka phat jana unko dikhaayaa.
3638,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein chaand ke 2 tukdey ho gaey they.
3639,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se 2 sahabi (Usaid-bin-Huzair aur Ibaad-bin-Bishr (Raziallahu anhu)) uth kar (apne ghar ( wapas huey. raat andherii thi lekin 2 charagh ki tarah ki koi cheez unke aagey roshni karti jati thin. phir jab ye donon (raastey mein, apne-apney ghar ki taraf janey ke liye) juda huey to wo cheez donon ke sath alag-alag ho gaee aur is tarah wo apne ghar walon ke paas pahunch gaey."
3640,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meri ummat ke kuchh log hamesha ghalib rahengey, yahan tak ke qiyamat ya maut aaeygii us waqt bhi wo ghalib hi hongey.''"
3641,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke meri ummat mein hamesha aik giroh aisa maujood rahega jo Allah Taala ki shariiat par qaaim rahega, unhein zaleel karne ki koshish karne waley aur isi tarah unki mukhalifat karne waley unhein koi nuqsan na pahuncha sakengey, yahan tak ke qiyamat aa jaeygi aur wo usi haalat par rahengey. Umer ne bayan kya ke is par Malik bin-Yukhaamir ne kaha ke Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha ke hamarey zamaney mein ye log Sham (Syria) mein hain. ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke dekho ye Maalik-bin-Yukhaamir yahan maujood hain, jo keh rahe hain ke unhon-ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke ye log Sham (Syria) ke mulk mein hain."
3642,"maine apne qabeele ke logon se suna tha, wo log Urwa se naql kartey they (jo abul-Jaad ke betey aur sahabi they) ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein aik Dinar diya ke wo uski aik bakri khareed kar ley aaein. unhon-ne us Dinar se 2 bakriyan khareediin, phir aik bakri ko aik Dinar mein bech kar Dinar bhi wapas kar diya aur bakri bhi pesh kar di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par unki tijarat mein barkat ki dua farmai. phir to unka ye haal hua ke agar mitti bhi khareedtey to usmein unhein nafa ho jata. Sufiyan ne kaha ke Hasan-bin-Umaara ne hamein ye hadis pahunchai thi shabeeb-bin-gharqada se. Hasan-bin-Umaara ne kaha ke shabeeb ne ye hadis khud Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) se suni thi. chunanche main shabeeb ki khidmat mein gaya to unhon-ne bataya ke maine ye hadis khud Urwa se nahi suni thi. albatta maine apne qabeele ke logon ko unke hawale se bayan kartey suna tha."
3643,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya khair aur bhalai ghodon ki peshani ke sath qiyamat tak ke liye bandhi hui hai. shabeeb ne kaha ke maine Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein 70 ghodey dekhey. Sufiyan ne kaha ke Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye bakri kharidi thi. shayad wo qurbani ke liye hogi."
3644,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ghodey ki peshani ke sath khair w barkat qiyamat tak ke liye baandh di gaee hai.''
3645,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke ghodey ki peshani ke sath barkat baandh di gaee hai.
3646,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghodey teen aadmiyon ke liye hain. aik ke liye to wo sawab ka zaria hain aur aik ke liye wo maaf yani mabaah hain aur aik ke liye wo wabaal hain. jiske liye ghoda sawab hai ye wo shakhs hai jo jihad ke liye usey paaley aur charaagaah ya baagh mein uski rassii ko (jis se wo bandhaa hota hai) khub daraaz kar de to wo apne us tool w arz mein jo kuchh bhi chartaa hai wo sab iske Malik ke liye nekiyan bin jati hain aur agar kabhi wo apni rassii tudaa kar do char qadam daud ley to uski leed bhi Malik ke liye baais sawab bin jati hai aur kabhi agar wo kisi nehar se guzartey huey usmein se pani pi ley agarche Malik ke dil mein usey pahley se pani pilaaney ka khayal bhi na tha, phir bhi ghodey ka pani peenaa uske liye sawab bin jata hai. aur aik wo aadmi jo ghodey ko logon ke samney apni haajat, parda poshii aur sawal se bachchey rehney ki gharaz se paaley aur Allah Taala ka jo haq uski gardan aur uski peeth mein hai usey bhi wo na bhooley to ye ghoda uske liye aik tarah ka parda hota hai aur aik shakhs wo hai jo ghodey ko fakhr aur dikhawey aur ahale-Islaam ki dushmanii mein paaley to wo uske liye wabaale-jaan hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se gadhon ke barey mein puchha gaya to aap ne farmaya ke us jaame' aayat ke siwa mujh par gadhon ke barey mein kuchh nazil nahi hua ( فمن يعمل مثقال ذرة خيرا يره * ومن يعمل مثقال ذرة شرا يره‏ ( ''jo shakhs aik zarra ke barabar bhi neki karega to uska bhi wo badla paaeyga aur jo shakhs aik zarra ke barabar bhi burai karega to wo iska bhi badla paaeyga.''"
3647,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaibar mein subah sawerey hi pahunch gaey. khaibar ke Yahudi us waqt apne phaawdey lekar (kheton mein kaam karne ke liye) ja rahe they ke unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aur ye kehtey huey ke Muhammad lashkar lekar aa gaey, wo qile' ki taraf bhaagey . iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath utha kar farmaya ''Allaahu-akbar khaibar to barbad hua ke jab ham kisi qaum ke maidan main ( jang ke liye) utar jatey hain to phir daraaiye huey logon ki subah buri ho jati hai.''"
3648,"maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! maine aap se bahut si hadison ab tak suni hain lekin main unhein bhool jata hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apni chadar phailaao, maine chadar phaila di aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se usmein aik lap bhar kar daal di aur farmaya ke usey apne badan se laga lo. chunanche maine laga liya aur uske baad kabhi koi hadis nahi bhula ."
